### FirstSaaS API Sample Requests

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api

---

## Authentication Requests

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

---

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123"
}

@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

---

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

## Product Requests

### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

---

### Get All Products with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?category=electronics&sort=price&order=asc

---

### Get Product By ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/prod_001

---

### Create Product (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Laptop",
  "price": 999.99,
  "description": "High-performance laptop",
  "image": "laptop.jpg",
  "category": "Electronics",
  "stock": 50
}

---

## Cart Requests

### Get Cart
GET {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### Add to Cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "prod_001",
  "quantity": 2
}

---

### Remove from Cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cart/prod_001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

## Admin Requests

### Get Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### Get User List (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

### Get Order List (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

---

## Error Handling Examples

### Invalid Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

---

### Weak Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "weak",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

---

### Unauthorized Access
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats

---
